Package: simPH
Title: Tools for simulating and graphing quantities of interest estimated using
    Cox Proportional Hazards models.
Description: The package simulates and plots, polynomial hazards,
    non-proportional hazards (relative hazards, first differences, and hazard
    ratios), and stratified survial curves from Cox Proportional Hazard models.
Version: 0.03
Date: 2013-02-12
Author: Christopher Gandrud
Maintainer: Christopher Gandrud <christopher.gandrud@gmail.com>
URL: http://christophergandrud.github.com/simPH/
BugReports: https://github.com/christophergandrud/SimPH/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 2.15.2)
Imports:
    MSBVAR,
    reshape2,
    plyr,
    ggplot2,
    survival,
    gridExtra
License: GPL (>= 2)
Collate:
    'tvc.R'
    'coxsimLinear.R'
    'coxsimtvc.R'
    'coxsimPoly.R'
    'coxsimInteract.R'
    'ggfitStrata.R'
    'gglinear.R'
    'ggtvc.R'
    'ggpoly.R'
    'GolubEUPData.R'
    'CarpenterFdaData.R'
